}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Toshkentda buyurtma asosida logotipli soatlar: premium sovg'a\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/logotipli-soat-korporativ-sovgalar-toshkent\"}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-8\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz\">Graver.uz</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 truncate max-w-xs\">Toshkentda buyurtma asosida logotipli soatlar: premium sovg&#x27;a</li></ol></nav><header class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">Toshkentda buyurtma asosida logotipli soatlar: premium sovg&#x27;a</h1><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500\"><time dateTime=\"2026-02-14\">13-fevral, 2026</time><span>1<!-- --> <!-- -->daqiqa o&#x27;qish</span><span>Graver.uz</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/blog/logotipli-soat-korporativ-sovgalar-toshkent.jpg\" alt=\"Toshkentda buyurtma asosida logotipli soatlar: premium sovg&#x27;a\" class=\"w-full aspect-video object-cover\" loading=\"eager\"/></div><article class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p>Logotipli soatlar rahbarlar, hamkorlar va eng yaxshi xodimlar uchun maqomli sovg&#x27;a formatidir. U ham minnatdorchilik, ham uzoq muddatli hamkorlik qiymatini ko&#x27;rsatadi.</p>\n<h2>Qaysi holatlarda mos keladi</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Kompaniya yubileyi va mukofotlash marosimlari</li>\n<li>VIP-mijozlar va asosiy hamkorlar uchun sovg&#x27;alar</li>\n<li>Yopiq tadbirlar va rasmiy uchrashuvlar</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Ishlab chiqarishda muhim bosqichlar</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Aniq maket va oldindan vizual ko&#x27;rinish</li>\n<li>Maqsadli auditoriyaga mos model tanlash</li>\n<li>Gravyura va qadoq sifatini yakuniy tekshiruv</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Soat modellari katalogi kerakmi?</strong> Sizga mos personalizatsiya variantlarini tayyorlaymiz.</p>\n<h2>Bog&#x27;liq maqolalar</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/mijoz-hamkorlar-uchun-sovgalar-vip\">Mijoz va hamkorlar uchun VIP sovg&#x27;alar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/xodimlar-uchun-sovgalar-hr-qollanma\">Xodimlarni mukofotlash sovg&#x27;alari</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/it-kompaniyalar-uchun-merch-toshkent\">IT kompaniyalar merchi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/banklar-va-fintex-uchun-sovgalar-toshkent\">Banklar va fintex uchun sovg&#x27;alar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/logotipli-soat-korporativ-sovgalar-toshkent\">Logotipli premium soatlar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/korporativ-tadbirlar-uchun-sovgalar-toshkent\">Korporativ tadbir sovg&#x27;alari</a></li>\n</ul></article><section class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">O&#x27;xshash maqolalar</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/mijoz-hamkorlar-uchun-sovgalar-vip\">Mijozlar va hamkorlar uchun sovg&#x27;alar: Toshkentda VIP korporativ sovg&#x27;alar</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Mijoz va hamkorlar uchun sovg&#x27;ani qanday tanlash: maqom, shaxsiylashtirish, qadoqlash. Gravyura, ishlab chiqarishdan oldin maket, muddatlar.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/xodimlar-uchun-sovgalar-hr-qollanma\">Xodimlarga sovg&#x27;alar: korporativ suvenirlar bo&#x27;yicha HR-qo&#x27;llanma</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Toshkentda xodimlarga sovg&#x27;alarni qanday tanlash. HR uchun g&#x27;oyalar, byudjetlar, muddatlar. Graver.uz dan shaxsiylashtirilgan gravyurali sovg&#x27;alar.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/it-kompaniyalar-uchun-merch-toshkent\">Toshkentdagi IT-kompaniyalar uchun merch: Qanday qilib ajralib turish va HR-brendni kuchaytirish</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Toshkentdagi IT-kompaniyalar uchun premium merch: xudi, powerbank, welcome pack va lazerli gravyura. Ishlab chiqarishdan oldin maket.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/banklar-va-fintex-uchun-sovgalar-toshkent\">Toshkentdagi banklar va fintex uchun korporativ sovg&#x27;alar: VIP, maqom</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Banklar, sug&#x27;urta va fintex uchun premium korporativ sovg&#x27;alar: VIP to&#x27;plamlar, Parker ruchkalari, gravyurali charm buyumlar. Maket oldindan tasdiqlanadi.</p></article></div></section><div class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8\"><a class=\"text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition flex items-center\" href=\"/uz/blog\">← <!-- -->Blogga qaytish</a></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800 mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">Toshkentda biznes uchun premium lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik va brendlash</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Navigatsiya</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz#services\">Xizmatlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/catalog-products\">Mahsulotlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/contacts\">Aloqa</a></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Aloqa</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">+998 77 080 22 88</a></li><li><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">+998 97 480 22 88</a></li><li><a href=\"https://t.me/GraverAdm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">Telegram</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm\">Toshkent, Mukimiy ko&#x27;chasi</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-800 mt-8 pt-8 text-center\"><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Graver.uz. <!-- -->Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan<!-- -->.</p></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-68f22649503f8e75.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><scri